      "role": "user",
      "content": "rest? how am i supposed to rest when everyone is waiting for me to explain why i ruined our lives? the debt follows me everywhere. even if i sleep, i just wake up to the same reality. it feels like the walls are closing in. i feel like i'm just a ghost walking around a life that doesn't belong to me anymore.",
